#	Configuration file for the monopole test

REQUIRES Driver
REQUIRES physics/Hydro
REQUIRES physics/Eos/EosMain/Gamma

D sim_dens Constant density state
D sim_pres Constant Pressure state
D sim_velx Constant x-velocity
D sim_vely Constant y-velocity
D sim_velz Constant z-velocity
D sim_magx x-component of B-field
D sim_magy y-component of B-field
D sim_magz z-component of B-field
PARAMETER sim_dens  REAL  1.0  [0 to ]
PARAMETER sim_pres  REAL  0.6  [0 to ]
PARAMETER sim_velx  REAL  0.0
PARAMETER sim_vely  REAL  0.0
PARAMETER sim_velz  REAL  0.0
PARAMETER sim_magx  REAL  0.0
PARAMETER sim_magy  REAL  0.0
PARAMETER sim_magz  REAL  0.0

D sim_rG Cutoff radius of the perturbation
PARAMETER sim_rG  REAL  0.2
